Title: Misdeeds in Moonbrook
Description:
Moonbrook? What is this Count Clessington doing at my home?!

It can't be anything good. I'll signal Shaw.

<Vanessa glances at Cecilia Clessington.>

She might make for a good hostage. Let's bring the rich girl, too.

Meet us there.
ObjectivesText: Meet Vanessa and Shaw in Moonbrook in Westfall.
